# Project Structure

This is a Next.js application for a requirements analysis and review tool. The main components are organized as follows:

## Core Components

- [app/page.tsx](mdc:app/page.tsx) - Main application page with layout and state management
- [app/layout.tsx](mdc:app/layout.tsx) - Root layout component with metadata and global styles

## Layout Components

- [app/components/layout/Header.tsx](mdc:app/components/layout/Header.tsx) - Application header with title and user info
- [app/components/layout/Sidebar.tsx](mdc:app/components/layout/Sidebar.tsx) - Collapsible sidebar with navigation
- [app/components/layout/MainContent.tsx](mdc:app/components/layout/MainContent.tsx) - Main content area with tabs

## Feature Components

- [app/components/features/upload/UploadPanel.tsx](mdc:app/components/features/upload/UploadPanel.tsx) - Document upload interface
- [app/components/features/analysis/AnalysisPanel.tsx](mdc:app/components/features/analysis/AnalysisPanel.tsx) - Document analysis interface
- [app/components/features/review/ReviewPanel.tsx](mdc:app/components/features/review/ReviewPanel.tsx) - Document review interface
- [app/components/features/results/ResultsPanel.tsx](mdc:app/components/features/results/ResultsPanel.tsx) - Analysis results display
- [app/components/features/report/ReportPanel.tsx](mdc:app/components/features/report/ReportPanel.tsx) - Final report generation

## Types and Schemas

- [app/types/document.ts](mdc:app/types/document.ts) - TypeScript types and Zod schemas for document handling
- [app/types/analysis.ts](mdc:app/types/analysis.ts) - Types for analysis results and rules
- [app/types/review.ts](mdc:app/types/review.ts) - Types for review process and issues

## API Routes

- [app/api/upload/route.ts](mdc:app/api/upload/route.ts) - Document upload endpoint
- [app/api/analyze/route.ts](mdc:app/api/analyze/route.ts) - Document analysis endpoint
- [app/api/review/route.ts](mdc:app/api/review/route.ts) - Document review endpoint
- [app/api/report/route.ts](mdc:app/api/report/route.ts) - Report generation endpoint

## UI Components

- [components/ui/button.tsx](mdc:components/ui/button.tsx) - Reusable button component
- [components/ui/card.tsx](mdc:components/ui/card.tsx) - Card container component
- [components/ui/tabs.tsx](mdc:components/ui/tabs.tsx) - Tab navigation component
- [components/ui/progress.tsx](mdc:components/ui/progress.tsx) - Progress indicator component
- [components/ui/table.tsx](mdc:components/ui/table.tsx) - Table component
- [components/ui/badge.tsx](mdc:components/ui/badge.tsx) - Badge component
- [components/ui/tooltip.tsx](mdc:components/ui/tooltip.tsx) - Tooltip component
